🎯 Panel 15 — ON‑TRACK Gauge (IMPORTANT)
This is the one you specifically asked for.

Logic:

`
OnTrack = CAC max <= (Full pack when new * 0.70)
`

OR if using thresholds:

- Green = CAC max ≥ 185 Ah  
- Yellow = CAC max 178–185 Ah  
- Red = CAC max ≤ 178 Ah  

Panel definition:

- Type: Gauge  
